  EffectDiscription_ENG: When one of your Digimon with a Tamer card in its digivolution
    cards digivolves into this card in your hand, reduce the memory cost of the digivolution
    by 2. [When Attacking] If a card with [Hybrid] or [Insectoid] in its traits is
    in this Digimon's digivolution cards, this Digimon can digivolve into a Digimon
    card with [Insectoid] or [Ten Warriors] in its traits in your hand for a memory
    cost of 3.
